content.text:
You can get a noticeable typography and polish lift **today** without starting the SPA rewrite. The lever is [`relocation_jobs/static/styles.css`](relocation_jobs/static/styles.css): add tokens at the top, then swap the highest-traffic ad-hoc sizes to semantic classes.

## The approach: tokens first, migrate in layers

Right now sizes are scattered (`0.68rem`, `0.8125rem`, `0.92rem`, `1.2rem`, `1.35rem`…). Don't rewrite all 6,000 lines. Do this in one sitting:

### Step 1 — Add typography + spacing tokens to `:root`

Append to the existing `:root` block (after `--shadow-sm`):

```css
/* Type scale */
--text-xs: 0.75rem;      /* 12px — labels, meta */
--text-sm: 0.875rem;     /* 14px — secondary body, buttons */
--text-base: 1rem;       /* 16px — default body */
--text-lg: 1.25rem;      /* 20px — section titles */
--text-xl: 1.5rem;       /* 24px — page titles */

--leading-tight: 1.25;
--leading-normal: 1.5;
--leading-relaxed: 1.625;

--tracking-tight: -0.02em;
--tracking-normal: 0;
--tracking-wide: 0.04em;

/* Spacing scale (4px base) */
--space-1: 0.25rem;
--space-2: 0.5rem;
--space-3: 0.75rem;
--space-4: 1rem;
--space-5: 1.25rem;
--space-6: 1.5rem;
--space-8: 2rem;

/* Motion */
--duration-fast: 120ms;
--duration-normal: 180ms;
--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
```

### Step 2 — Wire body + headings to tokens

```css
body {
  font-size: var(--text-base);
  line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  /* keep existing font-family, background, etc. */
}

.app-title {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
}

.page-title {  /* reuse for admin/apply h1 */
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
  line-height: var(--leading-tight);
}
```

### Step 3 — Add semantic text utilities (use everywhere new)

```css
.text-xs   { font-size: var(--text-xs); line-height: var(--leading-tight); }
.text-sm   { font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: var(--leading-normal); }
.text-base { font-size: var(--text-base); line-height: var(--leading-normal); }
.text-muted { color: var(--muted); }
.text-label {
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}
.tabular-nums { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
```

Then replace the worst offenders first — header selects, badges, stat labels — instead of hunting every `font-size` in the file.

---

## UX polish you can apply in the same pass

### 1. Global focus rings (2 rules, big a11y win)

Today only filter toggles and country chips have `focus-visible`. Add:

```css
:focus { outline: none; }
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
button:focus-visible,
a:focus-visible,
select:focus-visible,
input:focus-visible,
textarea:focus-visible {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-soft);
}
```

### 2. Respect reduced motion

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

### 3. Better empty states (board is the visible one)

[`App.jsx`](frontend/src/App.jsx) currently renders a flat string. Structure it:

```jsx
<div className="empty">
  <p className="empty-title">No companies on this page</p>
  <p className="empty-hint text-sm text-muted">
    Try another page or turn off a filter.
  </p>
</div>
```

CSS:

```css
.empty {
  padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-4);
  /* keep existing border/surface */
}
.empty-title {
  font-size: var(--text-base);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
}
.empty-hint { max-width: 28rem; margin: 0 auto; }
```

Same pattern for company-card empty messages in [`CompanyCard.jsx`](frontend/src/CompanyCard.jsx).

### 4. Unify transitions via token

Find-replace the mix of `0.12s`, `0.15s`, `0.18s`, `0.2s` on interactive elements:

```css
transition: background var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out),
            border-color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
```

### 5. Touch polish (already partly there)

You have `@media (max-width: 720px)` and `pointer: coarse` rules. After tokenizing spacing, bump header/button `min-height` to `2.75rem` (44px) consistently — several button classes still sit below that.

### 6. Kill inline style escape hatches

[`CompanyCard.jsx`](frontend/src/CompanyCard.jsx) has `style={{ fontSize: "0.8rem", fontWeight: 500 }}` on the careers link — move to `.company-careers-link { font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 500; }`.

---

## What to migrate first (highest visual ROI, ~2–3 hours)

| Priority | Area | Files |
|----------|------|-------|
| 1 | Page chrome | `.app-title`, `.header-select`, `.header-*-btn` in `styles.css` |
| 2 | Company/job cards | `.company-card`, `.position-card`, `.badge` |
| 3 | Board toolbar | `.board-toolbar`, `.filter-btn`, pagination |
| 4 | Dialogs | `.dialog`, `.dialog-btn` |
| 5 | Admin/apply/company | lower traffic; do when you touch those pages |

---

## Deploy checklist after CSS/JS changes

1. Bump `?v=` on `styles.css` in **all four** HTML shells (`index`, `company`, `apply`, `admin`) — versions currently drift (v39 vs v51 etc.).
2. If you change React: `cd frontend && npm run build`.
3. Hard refresh (`Cmd+Shift+R`) locally; `./scripts/ec2_app_deploy.sh sync` for production.

---

## What *not* to do "just now"

| Skip for now | Why |
|--------------|-----|
| Light theme | Needs full token pairs + testing every badge/ATS ring |
| shadcn / Tailwind | Build pipeline change; belongs in SPA Phase 0 |
| Line-by-line `styles.css` rewrite | Diminishing returns; you'll delete the file in the SPA |
| Moving `events.js` into React | Architecture work, not polish |

---

## Suggested "just now" PR scope

One focused PR (~150–250 lines touched):

1. Tokens + utilities + focus-visible + reduced-motion in `styles.css`
2. Migrate header + card + badge typography to tokens
3. Structured empty state in `App.jsx` + CSS
4. Sync cache-buster `?v=` across all HTML files
5. Remove one inline style in `CompanyCard.jsx`

That's visible polish without blocking on the 8–10 week SPA track — and the tokens carry forward into the rewrite.

